dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until GR (days)",
    "PO quantity less than PReq quantity (%)",
    "GR later than planned req date (%)",
    "Final issue indicator and withdrawal qty less than planned (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Goods receipt posted for purchase order items") 
        	AS "Time until GR (days)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Purchase order quantity less than purchase requisition quantity") 
        	AS "PO quantity less than PReq quantity (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Goods receipt later than planned requirements date") 
        	AS "GR later than planned req date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Components with final issue indicator and withdrawal quantity less than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Final issue indicator and withdrawal qty less than planned (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
	GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
